                    <li> A user can only place one review per restaurant (however they can edit or delete &recreate their review). </li><br>
                </ul>
            </li>
                
            <li>To moderate content, certain admin accounts will be created. They are meant for content moderation - so they cannot create any campground or add comments. </li> <br>
                
            <li>To prevent misrepresentation of someone's review by admin users, admin users are only granted permission to delete a comment or campground. </li> <br>

            <li>Users can also change their password in their profile page. </li><br>

            <li>Also, there is an option to reset password via email if incase a user forgets their password. <br>
            
